item.title: Can someone help me pleas?
item.dc:creator: @sonjichan sonjichan
item.description:
@sonjichan wrote:

looks at one star… Oh I see you download the client and play with hybridscape till you need help… then you come crawling back… lol jk

Use ::pickup **** (amount)

no matter the number of the ID code it must be 4 digits. So if you were picking up money like 100k it would be

::pickup 0995 100000

now if you wanted to pick up say… a party hat it would be… ::pickup 1054 1 or if you wanted 100 party hats in noted form it would be ::pickup 1055 100

That should do it…
